In the Matter of William F. Carrigan, Jr., a Suspended Attorney, Respondent. Grievance Committee of the Fifth Judicial District, Petitioner.

[— NYS2d —]

—Order of suspension entered. Memorandum: Respondent’s unexcused failure to appear or answer the petition constitutes a default. Present — Green, J. P., Pine, Wisner, Pigott, Jr., and Balio, JJ.
